Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.41,0:00:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I get too carried away?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The color changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.25,0:00:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.37,0:00:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Uh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.07,0:01:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fought brilliantly by pushing Vox Aura's abilities to the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Moid, and you have made a lasting impression on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fox...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.39,0:01:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vox Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.02,0:01:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the name of that Ovid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's its name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.16,0:01:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.36,0:01:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This robot is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.15,0:01:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think it would be that easy to pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.87,0:01:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.82,0:01:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It moves just the way I want it to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's red.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hit my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.45,0:01:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.37,0:01:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Tadokoro, the Fleet Captain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to brief you before your next mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.83,0:02:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next? There's going to be more?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.04,0:02:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woof.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I... go to the restroom first?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.33,0:03:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1027,160)\fnPrototype\bord0}{TS}{\fad(500,500)\c&HFDFDFD&}Kamogawa Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1030,163)\fnPrototype\bord2\blur3}{TS}{\c&H605649&\3c&H605649&\fad(500,500)}Kamogawa Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Izo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:03:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:04:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait. Array's Ovid isn't responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means one of us has to go and rescue him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy Ovid signal was like nothing we've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that they brought out the Vox?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't rule that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they already had the Vox,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.14,0:04:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's possible "Memoria" has been achieved as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they've found a pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the more the reason for me to head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the best Ovid pilot in De Metrio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.36,0:04:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the power of the Vox to crush Le Garite is our destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No time like now to check out the power
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the legendary weapon which we'll ultimately possess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if I don't come back, get out and save yourself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:04:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was tricked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.74,0:05:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was totally tricked!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one told me that there was going to be a second time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she pretend to be my comrade just to get close to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.85,0:05:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to make me pilot that "Fox"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were those memories false too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.07,0:05:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that was real... I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it? I'm so confused!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fnLevenim MT\bord0\shad1.5\pos(634,8)\4c&HFFFFFF&\c&H4F534D&}Missed calls: Nakaizumi Yoko{change name order? it's currently in western.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! They're all from Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad2\blur1\fs100\frx4\fry0\pos(403,211)\frz358.685}{TS}{\c&HB7BBBA&}No service
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No service.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a single bar!{quit using AT&T}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean your cousin beat that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing that it's not moving, I guess it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did your cousin actually manage to pilot that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she could only ride a bicycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she actually got a scooter license.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not enough to pilot a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be the people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're hiding something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've spent five years trying to figure out the Ooparts with no success.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the guys here built a robot out of it in six months!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's got to be some secret to—!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, please don't leave me alone here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you planning to do if Kyono Madoka
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was unable to activate Vox Aura today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who've achieved Memoria with the Vox
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,become its one and only pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Vox Aura falls into enemy hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.39,0:07:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as we safeguard Miss Kyono Madoka,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have an even chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the same could be said if their positions were reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could have accelerated her organic response with the Vox,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it was risky, so I wanted to avoid doing that if at all possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, we really weren't prepared to take considerable steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm glad to see that everything worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And as a result, I also learned quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:08:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't give a damn about protecting this planet, inside that head of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protecting the Vox is the same thing as protecting Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whose idea was it to make the Vox fight on the front line?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapons from Earth are useless against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you take the Vox and get off of this planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Earth would fall under their sphere of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a future would be bleak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.99,0:08:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what now, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will taking our chances against them work a second time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging only from the performance of the craft,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it has power that surpasses the enemy's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest depends on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll have to take our chances after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.40,0:08:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you one last question?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this main force of your's really coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately. After the war on their side is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pilot has run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good. I'm completely lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks similar...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess it's a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.78,0:09:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too?!                               You too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pilot... or... rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:09:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kyono Madoka. And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Muginami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say Miss Muginami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm going to look over that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you go that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.85,0:10:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I wasn't trying to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. I understand how you feel.{I know that feel.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I wish I could help more
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,instead of forcing everything onto you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But all I can do is fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.03,0:10:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'm going to be able to put this on by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can you do it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure. I'll have to take my chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good answer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.19,0:11:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now listen calmly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An enemy has appeared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Presently, its location is 100 km southeast of Oshima.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's heading this way at Mach 2.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At this rate, the confrontation will be in three minutes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Three minutes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We will control the craft during Piercer Mode.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All you have to do is sit tight, like the last time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that last jolt an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jolt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe she's referring to what triggered the Form Change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It wasn't an accident. It was planned.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're going to do that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:12:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Correct.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kyono.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.98,0:12:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The future of our planet rests in your hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fad(0,160)}We're counting on you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't handle that kind of pressure right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole planet? But I've never even been to Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commencing Vox Aura A.I. Remote System check.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Codes 1 through 11 are clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pilot's heart rate, blood pressure, respiratory rate... all normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Opening barrier walls one and two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy unit two is approaching quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vox Aura will engage the enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in approximately 100 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A.I. Remote Systems are normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vox System is operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuttle locks are open.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check complete. All systems go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to get really nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Vox System is silent like the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just hope for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.97,0:13:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vox Aura, take off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}An Ovid signal...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's not Array's, so that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The Vox!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You should see the enemy straight ahead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see it... a black one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're going in head-on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell with it... charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Vox System suddenly started up
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and is overriding the A.I. Remote!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.68,0:14:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me she's now in control of the Piercer Mode as well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.43,0:14:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears the girl really is a perfect match for Vox Aura, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you take this more seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All stations, prepare for attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't it either! This place is too big!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're the real deal, then let's see how you'll handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vox Aura's power grid is failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the status of the pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her vital signs are normal,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.68,0:15:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the craft has shut down completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do it, milady?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.44,0:15:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fear the legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really accept the Vox in your current state?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what Array lost to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good! I can't see a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a crazy idea to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, being a pilot...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where are you now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside a robot...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting her on speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.04,0:17:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait... You're not surprised?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cell phones work in there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.89,0:17:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's that call coming from!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Within Pharos premises, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why are you piloting a robot?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, a lot of stuff happened, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. I wanted to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen to me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.18,0:17:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I almost drowned ten years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even remember it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like I met this robot back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the enemy unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.51,0:18:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Distance from Vox Aura, 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's inside that black smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... of all the places.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a marine archaeologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.77,0:18:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been snooping around ever since
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our foundation confiscated her research regarding Vox Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pilot's cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one opposed to Kyono Madoka piloting the Vox Aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This robot is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It moves according to my thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared at first, but I got the hang of it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was quite fun, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's not anymore?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, after giving it some thought...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy unit two, distance from Vox Aura, 130!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:19:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems a lot of people are placing their hopes on me to pilot this robot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live up to their expectations as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to disappoint anyone, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I started thinking about that, it stopped moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.44,0:19:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just who the hell do you think you are?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing's not moving because you're acting like you're doing them a favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I'm saying you have to feel grateful to them for letting you pilot that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.76,0:19:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you decided to do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then take responsibility for that decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if that bothers you, then quit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Sweats Club!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're so irritating!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right. You are absolutely right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:20:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It pisses me off hearing that coming from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.73,0:20:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It drives me nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Distance from enemy unit, 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At a distance of ten, nine,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}eight, seven,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}six, five, four,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vox System online!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the distance with the Enemy Unit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.81,0:21:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An unknown craft has broken through the atmosphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's it heading?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.81,0:21:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pincer attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.69,0:21:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirius, what are you—?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.19,0:21:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sit and watch this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're going to die, we'll die together!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.34,0:23:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.33,0:23:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.28,0:23:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do it and I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.38,0:23:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.49,0:23:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I make up my mind to do it, I go all out. That's my style!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.29,0:23:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.71,0:23:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're in?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.83,0:23:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Array?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.97,0:23:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? Well, I've been captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.22,0:23:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.05,0:23:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.39,0:23:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izo said that you look bad.
