Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.85,0:23:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(295,562)\fnPrototype\bord2\blur3}{TS}{\c&H141E21&\fad(500,0)\3c&H141E21&\1a20\3a20}Lan Blooms
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.40,0:23:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so blunt!
